<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>SkillBridge Account Activation</title>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-width: 100%;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
    }

    a {
      color: #000;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    table td {
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #0070f3;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 24px;
      background-color: #fff;
    }

    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0070f3;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-raduis: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Activate Your Account</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p> Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for registering with SkillBridge. To activate your account, please use the following activation code:</p>
      <h2> <%= activationCode %></h2>
      <p>Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes.</p>
      <p>If you did not register for a SkillBridge account, please ignore this email.</p>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at support@skillsbridge.com</a></p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
